    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is starting to brown, reduce the heat to medium-low</p><p>Add the <strong>diced onion</strong> and cook for 2 min or until starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1723822572522-x200.jpg",
