            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Once the onion is starting to soften, add a generous knob of <strong>butter</strong> with the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> diced chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> ground coriander </strong>and<strong> ground cumin</strong></p><p>Cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1723822587915-x200.jpg",
