            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>farfalle </strong>with your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and 500ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[750ml]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[1L] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Increase the heat to high and bring to the boil</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for 14-16 min, or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the pasta is cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Tip: Stir occasionally to stop it from sticking!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1723822628760-x200.jpg",
